column5: Are the roads closed North of Dryden?
Nick, It looks like the roads should be passable again, check out this weblink http://www.drydenobserver.ca/npage.phtml?poid=367424Mike
Yes, you can. I just talked to the camp I'm going to in Sioux Lookout yesterday and he said all the roads were open. Sioux Lookout area didn't get hit as bad from the storms.
